          "reviewBody": "Teachers teach professionally and take the learning of kids very seriously.\nLKG teachers are taking care of little ones very well.\n9th grade kids are active in extra curriculars as well. Good for overall growth of child. And also this school has presense in many places in India so it's a good choice for parents who may change their lives cation due to work frequently.",
