        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Casagrand International School - Perumbakkam"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Mythreyei Ravi Kumar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-02",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "In recent times, one of the best decisions we took for our son is joining him in Casagrand International School.\nOne of the best administration, environment and facilities can be seen in Casagrand school, perumbakam campus.\nThe principal ma'am, teachers are giving their best for the kids for an holistic development of the child. My son loves to go to school everyday.\nIf we have any query regarding academics or any other issues, we can get immediate response from the concerned teacher which helps us a lot. The way the teachers are conducting unit tests from the beginning is very much appreciated so that the children start to revise the topics from the beginning itself. Teachers will take care in each and every subject especially language part.\nThanks to the entire Casagrand Team especially the principal ma'am.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
