            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I studied in this school only a year because\n\nThe downs of this school\n\nAcademics 👎 not so good\n\nTeacher - see a guy had a fight with me so his parents complained and mam scolded me but when I complained on him mam said she will talk to him but\nNo\n\nStudents I mean not all but some are bad,rude and they talk in regional\nLanguage\n\nStudent discrimination teachers treat pair who study good different and bad different\n\nCorrupt stuff many people talk bad stuff and do bad things\n\nThe ups of this school\n\nCaring for small people\n\nOther activities and cultural festivals are done good\n\nCleanliness and hygiene\n\nSo school is good for below 6th students\n\nOne more comment don't join in this school worst ever teachers are rude and their teaching is ok ok",
